Okay.

06:04.813 --> 06:07.716
<i>The site of their supposed
childhood balloon ride,</i>

06:07.748 --> 06:10.217
<i>to see if any of
the seeds I planted today</i>

06:10.250 --> 06:11.719
<i>have taken root.</i>

