06:19.460 --> 06:22.730
<i>[soft dramatic music]</i>

06:22.963 --> 06:24.499
We might not be able

06:24.532 --> 06:27.702
to remember our past accurately
all the time,

06:27.734 --> 06:29.903
but at least we have
direct insight

06:29.936 --> 06:32.039
into our own mental states.

06:32.073 --> 06:33.775
We know how we feel,

06:33.808 --> 06:34.943
what we like,

06:34.975 --> 06:36.310
and why.

06:36.344 --> 06:37.712
Except we don't.

06:37.744 --> 06:41.316
Psychologists call
our tendency to overvalue

06:41.349 --> 06:43.785
how we explain our own behavior

06:43.818 --> 06:45.854
